application size : 4GB
5-7 : sonarlint, git, docker . . . => 100*7 => 700Mbs
100files * 500Kb => 50 MB
Dependencies(maven/gradle/ant) => 1-2Mb to 200mb
10 microservices: 200*2 + 20*50 => 1.5GB
2 MS: 50-100MB of in memory data => 200MB

